# fin — opinionated CLI agent harness
# Run: go build -o /tmp/fin . && vhs demo.tape

Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "export PS1='$ '"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "cd /Users/meain/dev/src/fin"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "./demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 75s
